trans-unit.source: Determines the output files for non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.
trans-unit.target: Anger utgående filer för icke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt referenser.

trans-unit.source: The `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` task searches for a special property set by the [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE for the list of project GUIDs and their associated outputs.
trans-unit.target: Den `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` uppgift söker efter egenskap som den [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE lista över projekt GUID och deras associerade utdata.

trans-unit.source: The IDE only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects and in this way separates [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references from non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] references.
trans-unit.target: IDE endast före löser icke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt och på så vis åtskiljer [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt referenser från icke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referenser.

trans-unit.source: The IDE returns the list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects as UnresolvedProjectReferences.
trans-unit.target: IDE returnerar listan över [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt som UnresolvedProjectReferences.

trans-unit.source: This enables the task to use more powerful [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mechanisms to manipulate just the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references, such as.
trans-unit.target: Detta gör att aktiviteten kan använda mer kraftfulla [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mekanismer för att ändra bara det [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt referenser, t.ex.

trans-unit.source: calling into specific targets of references to get the manifest file name, which would not be possible with a mixed list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] and non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.
trans-unit.target: anrop till specifika mål referenser till att hämta namnet på manifestfilen som ska en blandad lista med [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] och icke-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt referenser.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger en XML-sträng som innehåller löst projektet utdata.

trans-unit.source: An XML string containing resolved project outputs.
trans-unit.target: En XML-sträng som löst projektet utdata.

trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger löst referens sökvägar som bevarar de ursprungliga referensattribut projektet.

trans-unit.source: The resolved reference paths that preserve the original project reference attributes.
trans-unit.target: Löst referens sökvägarna som bevarar det ursprungliga projektet referera attribut.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets project reference items that are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger referens projektobjekt som finns i den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.

trans-unit.source: Since [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects, the project reference items that could not be resolved using the pre-resolved list of outputs are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] före löser icke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt, referens projektobjekt som inte kunde matchas med före åtgärdats listan över utdata finns i den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
